OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOwen Paterson: Wise to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freview MPs' consultancy    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fjobs, says minister        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A cabinet minister has backed calls for
OL,6, the rules on MPs' consultancy jobs to  
OL,7, be reviewed, in the wake of the row    
OL,8, over Tory MP Owen Paterson.            
OL,10,FMr Paterson was found to have used his 
OL,11,Fposition to lobby for two firms paying 
OL,12,Fhim - reigniting debates over MPs'     
OL,13,Foutside employment.                    
OL,15,FInternational Trade Secretary          
OL,16,FAnne-Marie Trevelyan said it would be  
OL,17,F"wise" to revisit the issue of second  
OL,18,Fjobs.                                  
OL,20,FBut she rejected a blanket ban, arguing
OL,21,FParliament would lose out as a result. 
